{"about_the_game":"<i>Pathologic: The Marble Nest</i> is a mood-piece created to acquaint you with the world of <i>Pathologic</i>. It\u2019s a self-contained short story that uses the same assets and premise and the main game, but works as a spin-off.<br><br>In terms of gameplay, The Marble Nest doesn\u2019t feature every in-game mechanic that you\u2019ll find in the real <i>Pathologic,</i> and is generally in pre-alpha state. It\u2019s not optimised, so brace yourself for long loading times, bugs, crashes, and other issues. Early alpha versions are not always exactly fun to play. Please be prepared.<br><br><strong>KNOWN ISSUES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>No saves. </strong>The Marble Nest only takes ~2 hours to play, but it's still something to keep in mind<br></li><li><strong>Walking glitches. </strong>Sometimes characters walk funny. Will be fixed soon<br></li><li><strong>Don't change resolution and visual settings when playing</strong>\u2014it will lead to visual glitches. It's strongly advised to choose the optimal settings before you get into the thick of it. Will be fixed</li></ul><br><strong>UNKNOWN ISSUES</strong><br>are best reported to <a href=\"mailto:support@ice-pick.com\">support@ice-pick.com</a>. Every bug report helps the development!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1489481829","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607730/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1489481829","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607730/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1489481829","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607730/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1489481829","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<i>Pathologic: The Marble Nest</i> is a m